  "detailed_description": "Avia corporation invites everyone to feel like the owner of an airline. The game that is an economic strategy where you need to reason and carefully consider every step towards building the airline of your dreams. In this game, a rational approach and strategic planning skill are important. <br><br>Possibilities:   <br>- use initial capital to buy or rent aircraft. with the development of the company, your income also grows. <br>- more than a hundred aircraft models that are generated randomly. <br>- selection of destinations in more than one hundred and forty cities around the world <br>- passenger flow accounting system depending on the population and popularity of the city <br>- construction of complex air routes with transfers<br> - the weather<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.mp4?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.mp4?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/aca0b6ad836240efd6a4a0306d775fc6.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/aca0b6ad836240efd6a4a0306d775fc6.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/aca0b6ad836240efd6a4a0306d775fc6.mp4?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/f0a02f35c70082fae8c275302cd69ed6.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/f0a02f35c70082fae8c275302cd69ed6.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/f0a02f35c70082fae8c275302cd69ed6.mp4?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Avia corporation invites everyone to feel like the owner of an airline. The game that is an economic strategy where you need to reason and carefully consider every step towards building the airline of your dreams. In this game, a rational approach and strategic planning skill are important. <br><br>Possibilities:   <br>- use initial capital to buy or rent aircraft. with the development of the company, your income also grows. <br>- more than a hundred aircraft models that are generated randomly. <br>- selection of destinations in more than one hundred and forty cities around the world <br>- passenger flow accounting system depending on the population and popularity of the city <br>- construction of complex air routes with transfers<br> - the weather<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/ffbebf9faf6386092e4d5b426545bd6b.mp4?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.poster.avif?t=1705268307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.webm?t=1705268307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289080/extras/863f7b25e40add85667e719b4c99f47a.mp4?t=1705268307